snippet.title: The Sims 2 Mansion and Garden Stuff Official Trailer
snippet.description: Create luxurious mansions and colorful gardens for your Sims with The Sims 2 Mansion and Garden Stuff! Choose from 3 all-new architectural styles—Moroccan, Second Empire, and Art Deco—to completely re-create your Sims homes into mansions.
